RETR
</keywords>
</info>

# Server-side
<reply>
# file%TESTNUMBER contents...
<data nocheck="yes">
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Tue, 09 Nov 2010 14:49:00 GMT
Server: test-server/fake
